"In some distant sanctuary
set high in the sky"

495
00:24:57,250 --> 00:25:01,792
"Who is there above us
to whom we must bow or comply?"

496
00:25:02,083 --> 00:25:06,459
"Is any light greater,
any radiance akin"

497
00:25:06,709 --> 00:25:09,209
